				<div class="postbody">
				<a href="http://www.mysql.com/doc/en/Resetting_permissions.html" target="_blank">http://www.mysql.com/doc/en/Resetting_permissions.html</a>
<br />

<br />
Mabe you have looked at this but mabe you missed something. Here is my genral check list.
<br />
<ol type="1">
<br />
<li> Did the root password get wiped so there is no p/w
<br />
<li> Could the p/w have been reset to an earler p/w
<br />
<li> Can you make another user and grant <span style="font-style: italic">all privleges</span> eg. a new root
<br />
</ol>
<br />

<br />
Hopefuly that helps<br />
